# Icons Directory

This folder contains application icons and small graphical elements.

## Preferred Format
- SVG files are preferred for scalability and small file size
- PNG files for complex icons that don't work well as SVG

## Naming Convention
- Use descriptive names: `calendar-icon.svg`, `user-profile.svg`
- Include state variations: `menu-open.svg`, `menu-closed.svg`

## Common Icon Categories
- Navigation icons (menu, back, forward)
- Action icons (edit, delete, save, cancel)
- Status icons (success, error, warning, info)
- Feature icons (calendar, timesheet, reports, settings)
